## Choosing the Right Template

### Decision Matrix

| If your business... | Use Template |
|---------------------|--------------|
| Sells subscription software | SaaS |
| Sells products online (one-time or subscription box) | E-commerce |
| Connects buyers and sellers/providers | Marketplace |
| Generates leads for sales team | B2B Lead Gen |
| Is a hybrid (DTC subscription) | E-commerce + SaaS retention layer |
| Has multiple models | Build separate forecasts, then combine |

### Customization Tips

**All templates share core logic:**

1. Define your funnel stages (3-5 stages)
2. Identify stage transition events
3. Calculate conversion rates per stage
4. Apply appropriate attribution model per stage
5. Project forward with growth assumptions
6. Validate against historical actuals

**Customization areas:**

| Element | What to Customize |
|---------|-------------------|
| **Funnel stages** | Match your actual customer journey |
| **Conversion rates** | Use YOUR data, not just benchmarks |
| **Attribution models** | Adjust lookback windows for your cycle |
| **Metrics** | Add business-specific KPIs |
| **Timing** | Adjust for seasonality and sales cycle |

